Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:40.85,Next,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1859,1)\pos(960,800)}你不会想让我也为你而生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,斋君
